TODO

## Development

To set up this plugin locally, first checkout the code. Then create a new virtual environment:

    cd datasette-comments
    python3 -m venv venv
    source venv/bin/activate

Now install the dependencies and test dependencies:

    pip install -e '.[test]'

To run the tests:

    pytest
